reviews.name: Nickelodeon Spongebob Activity Table and Chair Set
reviews.reviewText: Kids love it,but the rubber caps on the legs do not prevent it from sliding all over the wood floors even when placed on a rug. It's best used in a corner.
reviews.title: sliding spongebob

reviews.name: Nickelodeon Spongebob Activity Table and Chair Set
reviews.reviewText: I got this for my grandson's 2 birthday. He loves it! He finally has a table and chair that fits his size, and he does everything on his table. Best present I ever got him. He is crazy about Spongebob, and it is very sturdy with locking legs on table and chairs.
reviews.title: My grandson loves this set

reviews.name: Nickelodeon Spongebob Activity Table and Chair Set
reviews.reviewText: WE BOUGHT THIS TABLE SET FOR OUR 6YR OLD & 2 YR OLD NOW THEY LOVE EATING SUPPER! CUTE AS IT CAN BE AND STURDY!!
reviews.title: CUTE!!

reviews.name: Nickelodeon Spongebob Activity Table and Chair Set
reviews.reviewText: I have a 4 year old who loves Spongebob. We need this table for him to do arts/crafts and etc. . .We plan on taking it for Christmas dinner so the little kids can eat at this table and therefore we will have more room at the adult table!
reviews.title: Wonderful

reviews.name: Nickelodeon Spongebob Activity Table and Chair Set
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for my son. He enjoys sitting at it playing or eating. I love this table and chairs. They are very sturdy and I like that they lock so no pinched fingers. I love it. This is a great item.
reviews.title: Spongebob Activity Table and Chair Set
